Summary: A blue moon like object just left of the moon in one photo and a beam of light in the next photo just to the right of the moon
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Gold Coast
There were no other sightings in Gold Coast on or around July 23rd 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsJust got to work seen the moon and thought I take a photo of it, about the 3 rd photo a blue moon like thing show up to the left of the moon. That night as I was looking at the photo the 4 photo has a beam of light to the right of the moon. Out of the 5 photo only 2 had something in it.
